    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a Saturday morning where the world is still asleep, and it\u2019s just you and this silver phantom cutting through the mist. This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule of elegance. Every curve of its silhouette tells a story of legacy, and the way the rich leather scent greets you is like an old friend\u2019s embrace. It hums with a quiet, confident power that demands attention without saying a word. To own this is to own a piece of automotive poetry\u2014a machine that doesn't just transport you, but transforms every journey into a grand event. It has been cherished, not just driven, waiting for a new guardian who understands that some spirits are simply too vibrant to be contained.",
